<p>Terms, conditions and date exclusions apply (see resort pages for details), and all offers are subject to availability. ‘New to Skiing’ packages are strictly for complete beginners only. Anyone who does not attend the free beginner ski/board classes provided will be judged not to be a genuine ‘beginner’, and will accordingly be asked to pay locally any upgrade price for the lift-pass and equipment-hire.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div></div>
</div>
<!--start right column-->
<div class="g3">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p style="color: #023761; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;">Win a ski lesson!</p>
<p><img src="/media/13048809/facebook-share.jpg" alt="Facebook -share" width="183" height="96" rel="442,231" /></p>
<p>To celebrate our 80th anniversary, we have 80 ski lessons to giveaway. All you need to do is 'Like' our <a href="https://www.facebook.com/inghams">Facebook page</a> and <a href="http://woobox.com/7xr3yp">click on the link</a> to answer the question. All correct answers will be put into our prize draw, good luck!</p>
</div>
<div></div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p style="color: #023761; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;">Free book and DVD</p>
<p><img src="/media/13048818/go-ski.jpg" alt="Go -ski" width="183" height="213" rel="183,213" /></p>
<p>We are proud to be a partner of the <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/special-offers/warren-smith-ski-academy">Warren Smith Ski Academy</a> - world famous for its expert ski coaching. A free copy of Warren’s excellent ‘Go Ski’ book and DVD is available to the first 100 guests booking one of our ‘New to Skiing’ packages. Simply book your holiday, and then email your booking reference number to: <a href="mailto:marketing@inghams.co.uk">marketing@inghams.co.uk</a></p>
</div>
<div></div>
<div style="color: #ffffff; text-align: left; background-color: #023761; border-top: 1px solid #f4f4f4; border-bottom: 1px solid #c4c4c4; padding: 10px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: #f4f4f4 #e4e4e4 #c4c4c4 #e4e4e4;">
<p style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;">Learn to Ski FREE!</p>
<p><br /><strong>LEARN TO SKI FREE IN LAPLAND</strong></p>
<p>The first 20 beginners* booking holidays departing 11 Jan – 8 Feb to <a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi">Levi</a> (all properties) and to Ylläs (<a data-udi="umb://document/3afff877d41a4e3db0dd313844ee3446" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3afff877d41a4e3db0dd313844ee3446}" title="Yllas Saaga Spa Hotel">Ylläs Saaga Hotel</a> &amp; <a data-udi="umb://document/d6a5b04bc7044b2faaf1e005d8d9bc7c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d6a5b04bc7044b2faaf1e005d8d9bc7c}" title="Yllas Saaga Apartments">Apartments</a> only) will receive a FREE Learn to Ski/Snowboard package worth £225, including 7 days equipment hire, 5 days x 1½ hours ski school, and a 7-day lift-pass.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>LEARN TO SKI FREE IN SLOVENIA</strong></p>
<p>We have 25 FREE Learn to Ski / Snowboard* packages to give away in <a data-udi="umb://document/71c7bd573f214a32ada6ee90c9f2d269" href="/{localLink:umb://document/71c7bd573f214a32ada6ee90c9f2d269}" title="Kranjska Gora">Kranjska Gora</a>, valid on all departure dates in January. Packages include 6 days equipment hire, 6 days x 2 hours ski-school, and a 3-day lift-pass, saving you £189 per person!</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>LEARN TO SKI FREE IN CANADA</strong><br />The first 20 first-time* skiers booking any holiday in <a data-udi="umb://document/0c45d07f55a64313a6e4bc714b58b52d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0c45d07f55a64313a6e4bc714b58b52d}" title="Whistler">Whistler</a> during 10-24 Jan or 7-21 March will receive a FREE Learn to Ski/Snowboard package, including 3 days equipment hire, ski-school and a 3-day lift-pass, saving you up to £225 per person.</p>
<p style="font-size: 10px;">*IMPORTANT: The above offers are strictly open to absolute beginners only, and are subject to availability / max. 2 free places per booking. Anyone who does not attend the free beginner ski classes provided will be judged not to be a genuine ‘beginner’, and will accordingly be asked to pay locally for the lift-pass and equipment-hire.</p>
</div>
<div></div>
<div style="text-align: left; background-color: #ffffff; border-top: 1px solid #f4f4f4; border-bottom: 1px solid #c4c4c4; padding: 10px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: #f4f4f4 #e4e4e4 #c4c4c4 #e4e4e4;">
<p style="color: #023761; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;">Exclusive special offer</p>
<p><a href="/{localLink:84fae36d-9062-4da0-8304-459cbe9cd4da}" title="Skiplex"><img src="/media/13049159/large-skiplex.png" alt="" width="183" height="" /></a><br />The Skiplex slopes at Reading, Basingstoke and Chiswick provide a great chance to get your ski legs back in shape before your holiday. Their revolutionary revolving ski slope creates an effectively ‘endless piste’, with no drag-lifts, none of the ‘stop-start’ frustration some skiers feel on short indoor slopes, and the slope’s speed and gradient can be varied to suit your ability level.</p>
<p><strong>Book your holiday by 31st October 2014 to qualify for a FREE 1 hour session</strong> for max. 3 skiers per booking, worth up to £120. (Any additional guests on the booking can buy one / get one half-price.) For full details and to see the Skiplex video, <a href="http://blog.inghams.co.uk/ski/learn-ski-skiplex/">click here</a>.</p>
</div>
